{"tid":218593,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲同我一樣覺得自己有暴力傾向？","createTime":"2017-04-26T15:24:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-26T15:44:28.000Z","uid":89953,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6def788df255f6ec9ad16297b91e71a6f638f4d7","tid":218593,"uid":89953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T15:24:21.000Z","msg":"我覺得自己有暴力傾向。<br />\n係心情唔好，煩躁，唔耐煩嘅時候，我就好想打鳩令我有呢啲心情嘅人。<br />\n好多時候同細佬嗌嗌下交，都係我出手打佢，仲要係想打死佢咁濟，差啲連工具都用埋。<br />\n最近因為group project同啲groupmates好唔夾，我用黑面去忍住自己唔出手打佢地，差啲連街外人都打埋。<br />\n我覺得自己好無用，管理唔到自己情緒，但係每次火起上黎，我真係控制唔到自己。<br />\n<br />\n點解我會咁，我可以點做？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f5cf01a53677d3f081abc3eb747fa562b95b285","tid":218593,"uid":8264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T15:31:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"254b7f265a42d222e7a4cdcdbb745029a3e7534e","tid":218593,"uid":89953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T15:34:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇吓醫生好喎</blockquote><br />\n心理醫生？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e620ee093764e22f1d872f84c41ad2ab91b3a6d3","tid":218593,"uid":32298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T15:39:05.000Z","msg":"試下係每次就打人果陣唱多啦a夢"},{"pid":"61b0356d9dea9514276a07197bf5b888d7152af5","tid":218593,"uid":8264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T15:39:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f37afdcdac70ad951777ce7fb1645db1805390c0","tid":218593,"uid":89953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T15:42:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試下係每次就打人果陣唱多啦a夢</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我驚我會愈唱愈炆"},{"pid":"9790837b6134a3dad1f86c1d9f3286ad67614bcd","tid":218593,"uid":89953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T15:44:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪情緒得唔到宣洩？</blockquote><br />\n我每次都有同唔同嘅朋友傾訴，但係仍然唔可以減少我嘅憤怒。。。"}]}